high_descs: Go to your left, and then turn right to the counter with the soap.
Pick up the soap on the left.
Turn to your right and go to the sink
Wash the soap in the sink.
Turn around and go to the counter next to the sink.
Open the bottom left drawer and place the soap in.
Move to the counter left of the sink.
Pick up the soap on the left from the counter.
Bring the soap to the sink.
Wet the soap in the sink with water.
Bring the soap to the cabinet left of the sink.
Put the soap in the lower cabinet left of the sink.

high_descs: walk on over to the bathroom counter to the left of the sink

put the soap inside the sink and rinse it off, then pick the soap back up
